txt.en: 'These white Uruks must be the Bloodless, as Rûkhor called them. We would do well to defeat as many as we can now, while we have the element of surprise on our side. I believe that Rûkhor uses the goblins as fodder for empowering his Uruk-hai forces, making them a strategic target as well. Enter Kaslokroz and defeat as many of Rûkhor's forces as you can.'
Goblins and white Uruk-hai pledged to Rûkhor the Pale Herald threaten the expedition into Cirith Ungol.
Rûkhor's forces are camped in Kaslokroz in Cirith Ungol.\n\nYou should defeat Rûkhor's uruks and goblins.

'Excellent work as always, [placeholder]. By removing the fuel to power his dark sorcery, and the forces who benefit from it, we have dealt a blow to the Pale Herald's strength. However, we should not let our guards down yet. The Gúrzyul should never be underestimated.'
Legolas can be found near Kaslokroz, Rûkhor's encampment.\n\nYou should talk to Legolas.
